{"tid":861603,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解全世界得偉大既美帝國先有能力幫到香港?","createTime":"2018-10-14T09:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T23:09:56.000Z","uid":85461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e238a737dcfd0b22930e335888b139b37aefac1c","tid":861603,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T09:09:39.000Z","msg":"大家一齊拜侵神 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求佢保佑香港<br />\n<br />\n呢首歌你地唔識都應該聽過個旋律<br />\n歌頌偉大既侵總統<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0JL_upFmUvs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0JL_upFmUvs&d=zoZnPIsdRNAkNaKs3iul9jCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=eeeee63b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0JL_upFmUvs</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\nHail to the Chief we have chosen for the nation,<br />\nHail to the Chief! We salute him, one and all.<br />\nHail to the Chief, as we pledge cooperation<br />\nIn proud fulfillment of a great, noble call.<br />\n<br />\nYours is the aim to make this grand country grander,<br />\nThis you will do, that's our strong, firm belief.<br />\nHail to the one we selected as commander,<br />\nHail to the President! Hail to the Chief!﻿<br />\n<img src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2017/11/Donald_Trump_official_portraitt-640x800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetapixel.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2FDonald_Trump_official_portraitt-640x800.jpg&h=cfa09846&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/LC2JRsLemWk/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FLC2JRsLemWk%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=84a45bfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.newsweek.com/sites/www.newsweek.com/files/styles/full/public/2018/06/27/trump2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newsweek.com%2Fsites%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Ffull%2Fpublic%2F2018%2F06%2F27%2Ftrump2.jpg&h=85185cc0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22c647f60e733d1f1b1d642b5b5786692bd94f80","tid":861603,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T09:11:26.000Z","msg":"仲有副總統Mike Pence<br />\n全場演講用黎鬧支那<br />\n現代歷史上有邊個試過全場演講去鬧一個國家<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/english/news/china/speech-10052018125302.html/china-pence-100518.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fenglish%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Fspeech-10052018125302.html%2Fchina-pence-100518.jpg&h=e77b4ee4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e920650b39fca86000a65d8ad9af57a6921e37c0","tid":861603,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T09:12:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0JL_upFmUvs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0JL_upFmUvs&d=zoZnPIsdRNAkNaKs3iul9jCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=eeeee63b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0JL_upFmUvs</a>"},{"pid":"b3d31f2c9fbbb2623efdc037a28cafb8d82e1cb1","tid":861603,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:09:37.000Z","msg":"+"},{"pid":"8e38a094e87f77540b4fa722f66594d6878cb82c","tid":861603,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T23:09:56.000Z","msg":"+"}]}